{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/prensa-y-medios-de-comunicacion/","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"3ca7c612-ba73-5f5f-95b4-f67ff0ba62b1","html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a6324f76d0a450dec02c2dbf83f51453/08cc5/giralda_tv_dby2p0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"giralda_tv\"\n        title=\"giralda_tv\"\n        src=\"/static/a6324f76d0a450dec02c2dbf83f51453/08cc5/giralda_tv_dby2p0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a6324f76d0a450dec02c2dbf83f51453/08cc5/giralda_tv_dby2p0.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">giralda_tv</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>6 Junio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.giraldatv.es\">Giralda TV</a></strong></p>\n<p>La televisión municiapl de Sevilla, Giralda TV, publica un video sobre nuestro proyecto de viajar desde España hasta Japón. En el video sale una minientrevista que nos hicieron en el lugar de salida, Coria del Rio <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mDsD1S7m3_A\" title=\"Ver recorte de prensa\">Ver video en Youtube</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/27429c79717b721fd35980d3efe5fc1d/08cc5/informacion.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"informacion\"\n        title=\"informacion\"\n        src=\"/static/27429c79717b721fd35980d3efe5fc1d/08cc5/informacion.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/27429c79717b721fd35980d3efe5fc1d/08cc5/informacion.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">informacion</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>4 Junio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.diarioinformacion.es\">Diario Información de Alicante</a></strong></p>\n<p>El periódico Información de Alicante publica en su edición fin de semana un artículo sobre nuestro proyecto de viajar desde España hasta Japón. <a href=\"http://www.diarioinformacion.com/fin-semana/2010/05/31/a-fondo/reportajes/ruta-samurai/5365.html\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ef538c032839a48cb479ba72f57a9cec/08cc5/diario_sevilla.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"diario_sevilla\"\n        title=\"diario_sevilla\"\n        src=\"/static/ef538c032839a48cb479ba72f57a9cec/08cc5/diario_sevilla.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ef538c032839a48cb479ba72f57a9cec/08cc5/diario_sevilla.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">diario_sevilla</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>4 Junio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.diariodesevilla.es\">Diario de Sevilla</a></strong></p>\n<p>El periódico Diario de Sevilla publica un artículo en su edición online sobre nuestro proyecto de viajar desde España hasta Japón en moto. <a href=\"http://www.diariodesevilla.es/article/sevilla/717159/japon/gran/salto.html\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/59e349deb65d7b0d9c4dbf7ed23102ba/08cc5/elcorreo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"elcorreo\"\n        title=\"elcorreo\"\n        src=\"/static/59e349deb65d7b0d9c4dbf7ed23102ba/08cc5/elcorreo.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/59e349deb65d7b0d9c4dbf7ed23102ba/08cc5/elcorreo.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">elcorreo</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>4 Junio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.elcorreoweb.es\">El Correo de Andalucía</a></strong></p>\n<p>El periódico El Correo de Andalucía publica un artículo en su edición online sobre nuestro proyecto de viajar desde España hasta Japón en moto. <a href=\"http://www.elcorreoweb.es/095907/samurais/dejan/coria/rio/motocicleta\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/29abd846fadcb5f9fc9687c987f51ebf/08cc5/eitb.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"eitb\"\n        title=\"eitb\"\n        src=\"/static/29abd846fadcb5f9fc9687c987f51ebf/08cc5/eitb.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/29abd846fadcb5f9fc9687c987f51ebf/08cc5/eitb.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">eitb</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>18 Noviembre 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.eitb.com\">Radio Euskadi</a></strong></p>\n<p>En el programa de radio “La casa de la palabra” que dirige Roge Blasco, Joan fue entrevistado en directo acerca del viaje de la Ruta Samurai. <a href=\"./images/radio_euskadi.mp3\">Escuchar entrevista</a>. También han escrito un artículo en su blog. <a href=\"http://www.blogseitb.com/rogeblasco/2010/11/21/joan-mira-%E2%80%9Cla-ruta-del-samurai%E2%80%9D-en-moto-desde-coria-del-rio-en-sevilla-hasta-sendai-en-japon-tras-los-pasos-de-hasekura-tsunenaga/\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/78dc1d425c17651b085a420bd2e860df/08cc5/infoweek.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"infoweek\"\n        title=\"infoweek\"\n        src=\"/static/78dc1d425c17651b085a420bd2e860df/08cc5/infoweek.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/78dc1d425c17651b085a420bd2e860df/08cc5/infoweek.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">infoweek</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>10 Julio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.infoweek.biz\">InfoWeek</a></strong></p>\n<p>Esta página web especializada en productos innovadores publica un artículo sobre la tecnología RFID que utilizamos en el anuncio de nuestro patrocinador Piononos. <a href=\"http://www.infoweek.biz/la/2010/06/los-anuncios-comienzan-a-incorporar-la-tecnologia-rfid/\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b67f0bef8b254c2f9eb35cb0b59aa642/08cc5/idnoticias.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"idnoticias\"\n        title=\"idnoticias\"\n        src=\"/static/b67f0bef8b254c2f9eb35cb0b59aa642/08cc5/idnoticias.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b67f0bef8b254c2f9eb35cb0b59aa642/08cc5/idnoticias.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">idnoticias</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>4 Julio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.idnoticias.com\">IDNoticias</a></strong></p>\n<p>Esta página web especializada en tecnologías de identificación publica un artículo sobre la tecnología RFID que utilizamos en el anuncio de nuestro patrocinador Piononos. <a href=\"http://www.idnoticias.com/2010/06/14/los-anuncios-comienzan-a-incorporar-la-tecnologia-rfid\" title=\"Ver el artículo\">Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/753d79219dc77da652381b25cea0092f/08cc5/puro_marketing.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"puro_marketing\"\n        title=\"puro_marketing\"\n        src=\"/static/753d79219dc77da652381b25cea0092f/08cc5/puro_marketing.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/753d79219dc77da652381b25cea0092f/08cc5/puro_marketing.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">puro_marketing</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>4 Julio 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.puromarketing.com\">PuroMarketing</a></strong></p>\n<p>Esta página web especializada en marketing publica un artículo sobre la tecnología RFID que utilizamos en el anuncio de nuestro patrocinador Piononos. <a href=\"http://www.puromarketing.com/12/7418/el-marketing-ya-incorpora-tecnologia-rfid.html\" title=\"Ver el artículo\"> Ver el artículo</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a28f258f561d7fbd1d9fec49262418f7/08cc5/granada.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"granada\"\n        title=\"granada\"\n        src=\"/static/a28f258f561d7fbd1d9fec49262418f7/08cc5/granada.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a28f258f561d7fbd1d9fec49262418f7/08cc5/granada.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">granada</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>25 Abril 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.granadahoy.com\">Granada Hoy</a></strong></p>\n<p>El periódico Granada Hoy publica una página entera sobre los viajes del granadino Vicente Malpica y sobre nuestro proyecto de viajar desde España hasta Japón. <a href=\"./images/diario_granada.jpg\" title=\"Ver recorte de prensa\"> Ver recorte de prensa</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9e0eb2a3e2a6a8414aa9b204ec2c05cd/08cc5/solo_moto.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"solo_moto\"\n        title=\"solo_moto\"\n        src=\"/static/9e0eb2a3e2a6a8414aa9b204ec2c05cd/08cc5/solo_moto.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9e0eb2a3e2a6a8414aa9b204ec2c05cd/08cc5/solo_moto.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">solo_moto</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>31 Marzo 2010 – <a href=\"http://www.solomoto30.com\">Revista SoloMoto</a></strong></p>\n<p>En la publicación nº 326, en la página 136 (Correo del lector), hablan sobre nuestro proyecto. Gracias! <a href=\"./images/solomoto_lector2.jpg\" title=\"Ver recorte de prensa\"> Ver recorte de prensa</a> | <a href=\"./images/solomoto_lector1.jpg\" title=\"Detalle del anuncio\">Detalle del anuncio</a></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 140px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/37bf149f5d9f8431a8ff44c57f6abd9f/08cc5/rac1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rac1\"\n        title=\"rac1\"\n        src=\"/static/37bf149f5d9f8431a8ff44c57f6abd9f/08cc5/rac1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/37bf149f5d9f8431a8ff44c57f6abd9f/08cc5/rac1.jpg 140w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 140px) 100vw, 140px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">rac1</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>25 Febrero 2010 – Radio en Cataluña – <a href=\"http://www.rac1.org\">RAC 1</a></strong></p>\n<p>RAC 1 habló sobre La Ruta del Samurái en uno de sus programas de radio. Gracias a ellos, la empresa de Walkis Midland se puso en contacto con nosotros para patrocinarnos. Gracias!</p>","fields":{"slug":"/prensa-y-medios-de-comunicacion/","prefix":"10 January 2010"},"frontmatter":{"title":"La Ruta Samurái por España","category":"samurai-route","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/a6324f76d0a450dec02c2dbf83f51453/4e5f3/giralda_tv_dby2p0.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/prensa-y-medios-de-comunicacion/","prev":{"id":"8adc8e02-ce3d-5f13-be81-a53a944b1296","fields":{"slug":"/el-proyecto/","prefix":"9 January 2010","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"El Proyecto","category":"samurai-route"}},"next":{"id":"0416c24e-168c-5ddd-b087-5438a4db10fc","fields":{"slug":"/la-ruta-samurai-por-espana/","prefix":"10 January 2010","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"La Ruta Samurái por España","category":"samurai-route"}},"source":"posts"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}